main_body:
Amendments to Directive 2002/55/EC
Directive 2002/55/EC is amended as follows:
(1) in Article 2(1)(b) the words ‘Lycopersicon esculentum Mill.’ are replaced by the words ‘Solanum lycopersicum L.’;
(2) in the table in point 3(a) of Annex II, the words ‘Lycopersicon esculentum’ are replaced by the words ‘Solanum lycopersicum L.’;
(3) in the table in point 2 of Annex III, the words ‘Lycopersicon esculentum’ are replaced by the words ‘Solanum lycopersicum L.’.
